      "originalText": "tmp/<hash>/{upper,work,root}  →  RUN via chroot /bin/sh  →  COPY FROM=<block>  →  WORKDIR\nAUTO-DEPS: detect package manifests → run npm / pip / go  →  finalize: mv upper → layers/<hash>\nBNEED blocks: executed but excluded from final image stack unless explicitly COPY'd",
